{\listtext	\'95	}12 to 16 lb turkey\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 \'bd heads garlic cloves peeled\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 Tbs. Paprika\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 Tbs. kosher salt\
{\listtext	\'95	}\'bd tsp black pepper\
{\listtext	\'95	}3 to 4 Tbs. Oil\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 Onions sliced into discs\
{\listtext	\'95	}7 bay leaves\
{\listtext	\'95	}Large bunch fresh Thyme, leaves attached to stems\
{\listtext	\'95	}You will also need:\
